 optical interactions can play an important\nrole in integrated optics and paves the way to an entire new class of photonic\nsystems that exploit the vectorial nature of light.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 2 Dec 2015 19:28:23 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 31 Jan 2017 17:27:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-02-01"}
